Implement the "fight" method in Arena.  

ASSUMPTIONS
character1 is always the attacker.
character2 is always the defender.
The attacker gets 100% of their attack attribute and 75% of their defense.
The defender gets 100% of their defense attribute and 75% of their attack.
The character with the greater total always wins.
The attacker wins in the event of a tie.